nodes.text: Journey to Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker: The Resistance
Journey to Star Wars: The Rise of Skywalker: The Resistance is a canon activity book written by Sally Little, with six sounds included. The book was published on October 4, 2019.
Follow the rise of the Resistance with this six-button sound book featuring story moments, lines of dialogue, sound effects, and a light-up lightsaber sound module.
